@model AnubisDBMS.Data.ViewModels.MantenimientoVM


@using (Html.BeginForm("AgregarMantenimiento", "Mantenimiento", new { }, FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "ui grid", id = "" }))
{
    <div class="eight wide column">

        <div class="ui raised segments">
            <div class="ui bottom attached raised menu">
                <div class="header item">
                    Nuevo Mantenimiento
                </div>
                <div class="right menu">
                    <button type="submit" class="item"><i class="save icon"></i>Guardar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ui compact raised segment">
                <div class="ui tiny form">
                    <div class="two fields">
                        @*<div class="six wide field">
                                <label>Tipo de Mantenimiento</label>
                                @Html.TextBox("test")
                            </div>*@
                        <div class="six wide field">
                            <label>Fecha de Mantenimiento</label>
                            <div class="ui labeled input">

                                <div class="ui label">
                                    <i class="calendar icon"></i>
                                </div>
                                @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.FechaMant, "{0:yyyy-MM-dd}", new { @class = "date-picker", @id = "Fecha-mant" })

                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="ui toggle checkbox" style="padding-left: 60px">

                            <input type="checkbox" name="Notificaciones">
                            <label>Recibir Notificaciones</label>

                        </div>
                        @*<div class="ui input" style="max-width:15% !important">

                                <input  type="text" />
                            </div>*@

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ui raised segment orange">
                <div class="ui form">

                    <div class="sixteen wide field">
                        <label>Descripcion del Mantenimiento</label>

                        @Html.TextAreaFor(m => m.Descripcion, htmlAttributes: new { style = "width: 100%; max-width: 100%;" })
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="five wide column">

        <div class="ui raised segments">
            <div class="ui bottom attached raised menu">
                <div class="header item">
                    Datos de contacto
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="ui compact raised segment">
                <div class="ui tiny form">
                    <div class="two fields">
                        <div class="six wide field">
                            <div class="ui labeled input">

                                <div class="ui label">
                                    <i class="mail icon"></i>E-mail
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="six wide field">
                            <div class="ui labeled input">

                                <div class="ui label">
                                    <i class="phone icon"></i> #Celular
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="">
                            </div>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

}


@section scripts{
    <script>

        $('.ui.checkbox').checkbox();
    </script>

}